# Shri Sowdeswari Women's College

'''Shri Sowdeswari Women's College is located near Kondalampatti Bypass in Tamil Nadu, India. Formerly called Salem Sowdeswari College''', it was coeducational from its founding in 1975 until academic year 2022/23, when it was converted to a women-only college.
